{
  "chapter": 30,
  "chapter_summary": "郭大路与燕七来到金公馆门前，发现大门上的门环竟是黄金铸成。燕七告诉郭大路，金大帅是江湖中有数的世家大族之一，以纯金兵器闻名，最善用的暗器是金弓神弹，一出手就是二十一颗纯金弹子，江湖中鲜有人能躲。燕七提议让郭大路去找金大帅比武，接住金弹子来换钱还债。郭大路起初拒绝，但在燕七的劝说下勉强答应。两人先以拜帖求见，却遭金公馆老门房嘲讽拒绝。郭大路气愤不已，燕七又想出新主意：让郭大路主动上门挑战。最终郭大路硬着头皮去赊账，为朋友甘愿丢面子。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这家人一定是个暴发户。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "暴发户？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只有暴发户才会做这种事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这种什么事？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这种简直可以叫人笑掉大牙的事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你错了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我哪点错了？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我就觉得很可笑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那只因为你不知道他是谁。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你真知道？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只可惜这种人现在却偏偏跟你有点关系吧？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么关系？他又不是我的债主！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那倒还不至于，我们还没穷到这种地步。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "也不是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁的脸红了？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我看你眼睛发花才是真的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我明白了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你明白了什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "噗哧",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "虽然不太美，却正是女人一见就喜欢的那种男人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你倒真是马不知脸长。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "无论你怎么说，反正我这次绝不上你的当。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "上什么当。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她若长得又年轻，又标致呢？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在我只想你做一件事，不知道你肯不肯？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你说。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只凭一点。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哪点？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就凭这条巷子原本就是他一个人的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看样子只怕是金大帅回来了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "金大帅是谁？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就是你说的那个财大气粗的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我果然没有说错吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有钱人并不见得就不是好人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但他凭什么要叫大帅？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看样子你好像也很佩服他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我能不能佩服他？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "能，当然能……可是我能不能不佩服他呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不能。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么不能？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你不是一向都很佩服你自己的吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嘿嘿。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嘿嘿。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嘿嘿是什么意思？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嘿嘿的意思就是我不相信。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你看见他就会相信。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我根本就不想看见他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是你却非去看他不可。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为你不去看他，就只有去看那些债主的脸色了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我知道你的脸皮还没有那么厚。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么你叫我去看他干什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你是说那位叫'石神'的老前辈？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你知不知道'石神'这名字是怎么来的？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为他只用石头做的兵器，而且用得很好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "答对了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是。只不过……他跟这金大帅又有什么关系呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "金大帅跟他一样，也是个怪人，用的兵器也很奇怪。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他用什么兵器？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他只用金子做的兵器，而且是纯金做的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "弹子也是金的？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "纯金。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不干，这种事我绝不干。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没有为什么，不干就是不干。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦……我明白了，你是怕……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我怕什么？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你当然不是怕他，只不过是怕胖而已。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "怕胖？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "疼起来就会肿，肿起来就胖了，胖起来就不太好看。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一个人若肿了起来，那才真的滑稽。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你到哪里去？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我最近饿得太瘦了，本来就要想法子变胖一点。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你难道想就这样冲进去，找人家去打架？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我还能用什么法子去跟人家打架？难道跪着去求他？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你就算真的跪着求他，他也未必会出手的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么法子？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你想想，要什么样的人才能令金大帅出手呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我想不出，也懒得想。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只有两种人？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哪两种人？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难道要我去把他的老婆抢来，先制造点仇恨？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哼哼，滑稽滑稽。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "幸好除此外，还有种法子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗯！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就在这里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你怎么知道？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你既看出来了，还不快去通报？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大醉侠也并不一定是天天要喝醉的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_men_fang",
      "speaker_name": "老门房",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么我劝郭大侠不如快回去的好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你为什么不给他两巴掌？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来你的脸皮并不太厚，比城墙还薄一点。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以我现在只想快点走，越快越好。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你急什么，我还有别的法子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你能不能不出别的主意了？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不能。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 424
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我能不能不听？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不能。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你真的认为这件事做得丢人？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这就对了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哪点对了？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "对。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "对。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在已经有几点是对的了？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 466,
      "line_end": 466
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "三点。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 468
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么你还有什么话说？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 470,
      "line_end": 470
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没有了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 472,
      "line_end": 472
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你还想不想听我的主意？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 474,
      "line_end": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "简直想得要命。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 476,
      "line_end": 476
    }
